dc_title_s: Mutsu Dewa kokugun kōtei zenzu; Hashimoto Gyokuransai.; Cover title has subtitle: Tsuketari Echigo hangoku
dc_description_s: Wood block print. Shows shipping routes. Oriented with north to the right. Relief shown pictorially. Includes descriptive list of daimyo. 1 map: col.; on sheet 91 x 145 cm., folded in covers 26 x 19 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
